{"tid":2120766,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"北京醫科大學校長《紐時》撰文 批美國處理疫情不當害死至親：喺中國就唔會死！","createTime":"2020-07-23T01:39:33.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-23T04:41:51.000Z","uid":1886,"like":3,"dislike":15,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"c8413f06075a48b5229a9902f78715e8c0415a69","tid":2120766,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-23T01:39:33.000Z","msg":"著名神經生物學家、北京首都醫科大學校長饒毅，在《紐約時報》撰文，講述叔叔饒厚華（音譯，Houhua，洋名Eric）在紐約死於武漢肺炎的經過，令其90歲父親饒緯華痛失至親。他引述父親表示「一旦厚華身處中國，便能保命」，又指家族12名在武漢親人，至今全部安全。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/international/20200723/BOFXBPVUEEF6G5CQT322PY4254/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20200723%2FBOFXBPVUEEF6G5CQT322PY4254%2F&d=DosFxDX7yTzXLN9Gri3QgAuBxQMtbc6xR8MkqxZcasw%3D&h=349b2fac\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20200723%2FBOFXBPVUEEF6G5CQT322PY4254%2F&h=9224c0bc\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/international/20200723/BOFXBPVUEEF6G5CQT322PY4254/</a>"},{"pid":"278d6b1833288846bde10c0d505e91ca5880d944","tid":2120766,"uid":1886,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-23T01:39:56.000Z","msg":"饒毅在文中講述了父親饒緯華一家顛沛流離的一生。他指，饒緯華1947年為了完成學業，留在南昌，父母則帶着弟妹、包括當時僅兩歲的饒厚華，前往台灣，未料中共1949年建政後，饒緯華與家人自此天各一方，緯華、厚華兩兄弟要到35年後，才在美國重逢。"},{"pid":"bd9721edf9422a1aa7b6a57caca6c86635f15f04","tid":2120766,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-23T01:40:16.000Z","msg":"後來，饒緯華成為胸肺科醫生，在上海執業，文革期間被流放到鄉村，1972年返回南昌，開始與海外家人通信。身在台灣的弟弟饒厚華，成為緯華與其他家人之間的密使。"},{"pid":"06695c1e8aaa7d5b15ebd3ef1b9b612be0d76f69","tid":2120766,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-23T01:40:36.000Z","msg":"70年代後期，饒厚華前往三藩巿留學，成為藥劑師並取得美籍；哥哥緯華則於1982年到加州大學三藩巿分校（UCSF）學術交流，兩兄弟得以重聚。緯華在三藩巿綜合醫院（現命名為Zuckerberg San Francisco General Hospital and Trauma Center）深切治療部接受訓練，回到中國後，他在江西設立省內首個深切治療部。饒毅表示，父親對在美國接受的教育和遇過的人，一直很感激。"},{"pid":"27169a1072159c305375ad38aad8ebb9d6d3e14d","tid":2120766,"uid":198278,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-23T01:40:41.000Z","msg":"on99<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6a71ad4ec0701c901c0af82eaafd257d72176fe3","tid":2120766,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-23T01:40:50.000Z","msg":"1985年，饒家逐漸移民到美國，包括在中國出身長大的饒毅及其弟弟。饒毅曾到加州大學三藩巿分校攻讀博士，成為知名神經生物學家，結婚生子，2000年入籍美國。直到2007年，他返回中國定居，2011年完成放棄美籍程序。"},{"pid":"d29bfa1c85155421a0ad16df33202eea8ca53728","tid":2120766,"uid":16057,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-23T01:41:04.000Z","msg":"漢奸<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"de9e9e7d60af678e1ad0bacdf644137e1b19b523","tid":2120766,"uid":41389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-23T01:41:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b76710ecfcb93906f08a0ef94bc828bed417d937","tid":2120766,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-23T01:41:25.000Z","msg":"饒毅形容，「911」恐襲發生後，美國時任副總統切尼（Dick Cheney）、時任國防部副部長伍夫維茲（Paul Wolfowitz）、切尼的幕僚長艾丁頓（David Addington）以及司法部顧問柳淳（John Yoo）組成「邪惡軸心」，違法地在伊拉克發動戰爭，在關塔那摩灣（Guant&aacute;namo Bay）設立「黑獄」，令他質疑美國並非心目中的「民主燈塔」而心生去意。"},{"pid":"068f99912649609ce449675d71475d37021f8620","tid":2120766,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-23T01:41:43.000Z","msg":"饒毅指，叔叔厚華自兩歲離開中國後，一生未返回中國。他紐約巿皇后區執業，今年3月確診患上武漢肺炎，估計是上班時遭別人感染。染疫後，他卧病在床長達兩個月，靠呼吸機維生，最終醫生認為他無法痊癒，拔除他的呼吸機，讓給其他有機會生還的病人。饒厚華在10日後、即5月20日病逝，終年74歲。"},{"pid":"6202c45c57bb8ecbce0789668df45c636c987c57","tid":2120766,"uid":62749,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-23T01:41:57.000Z","msg":"<strong>黑警套洗白片上左YOUTUBE,大家識做啦 (2)<br />\n</strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2120442\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2120442</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"red\">做完任再幫推</span>"},{"pid":"c2783dcc490819ccbb568f5ef6ebb6cf9b031d2b","tid":2120766,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-23T01:42:03.000Z","msg":"饒毅透露，父親饒緯華年幼時因母親死於輕病，立志從醫，成為胸肺科醫生，詎料90歲時再痛失親人，卻無力挽救。饒毅指，包括叔叔在內、其家族有6名親人在紐約，另外有12名親人在武漢，結果在武漢的親人全部安全，而叔叔身在「全世界軍力最強大、經濟最富裕、醫學最先進的美國」卻病逝。父親緯華則堅信，如果弟弟身在中國，必定能夠救回來。"},{"pid":"ffec32bc4683206d766c5744cdaf7d0a1c1e45aa","tid":2120766,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-23T01:42:18.000Z","msg":"饒毅批評，美國比中國足足多出兩個月時間，可以從中學習處理疫情，質疑美國的高感染率和高死亡率能夠避免。他又指疫情當前，中美兩國不旦沒有合作，反而在研究疫苗和治療方法上競爭。"},{"pid":"27536b58fb565a0351c8f783b1b5e06352a55929","tid":2120766,"uid":76960,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-23T01:42:27.000Z","msg":"咁你仲唔死番大陸？"},{"pid":"8049b21db38c25be9cbde74ef3af9408b201a2a2","tid":2120766,"uid":18048,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-23T01:42:56.000Z","msg":"Nmsl"},{"pid":"7be3279339e001064c810a204685abf429e00dca","tid":2120766,"uid":288505,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-23T01:43:17.000Z","msg":"咁仲唔快d接晒親屬回歸佢祖國<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/noodles.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b5621159d81670e76d10211a4d23ea7e6d97fc7a","tid":2120766,"uid":8308,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-23T01:43:37.000Z","msg":"係中國死左老豆你仲可以出黎撰文？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"488cf1b9fb76a17f77545d81466e0b495fc25d26","tid":2120766,"uid":149662,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-23T01:45:38.000Z","msg":"啱啦<br />\n絕對支持佢全家返中國"},{"pid":"0cfe90c9d4eeab7227fbd8e99340deaf1096cd5a","tid":2120766,"uid":83228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-23T01:45:39.000Z","msg":"睇吓呢種人<br />\n仲問點解唔合作<br />\n厚顏到"},{"pid":"84f925807d9f42a47b9447cab90fdcca6b37267c","tid":2120766,"uid":346701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-23T01:50:39.000Z","msg":"咁點解唔死返支國？"},{"pid":"18e44d35d6e66289111245f0a2058f93b273e89e","tid":2120766,"uid":66087,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-23T01:53:08.000Z","msg":"佢錯唔晒<br />\n<br />\n家姐係美國，依家就算咳晒都唔比你入醫院，因為已經full晒，一定要好嚴重先可以入 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7210fb44304cc00715aaae2cb07c44dcf4c57ec3","tid":2120766,"uid":3149,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-23T02:01:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"135d588479ab4a9f425053a1c9317d322a0522d3","tid":2120766,"uid":29153,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-23T02:03:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"adfd36f3d929c4038f5de9e11adbfb135b914bd6","tid":2120766,"uid":18251,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-23T02:05:06.000Z","msg":"咁咪全家全族返中國囉？多鳩餘"},{"pid":"d76f54db6805e6b966d4c3c35b9f8c46d6502f19","tid":2120766,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"adfd36f3d929c4038f5de9e11adbfb135b914bd6","tid":2120766,"uid":18251,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-23T02:05:06.000Z","msg":"咁咪全家全族返中國囉？多鳩餘"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-23T02:06:22.000Z","msg":"又指家族12名在武漢親人，至今全部安全。"}]}